pageProduct.name: SUP Fit Energy 65 Gummies
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Caffeine Energy Gummies for that 'get up and go' kind of energy.

ENERGY, SWEET ENERGY

For times when you want to order that extra coffee, snooze the alarm or hit that 3pm slump, reach for SUP FIT Caffeine Energy Gummies. Five SUP gummies equal one cup of coffee so you can choose how much of an energy kick you want; five for a big energy hit or one for a pick-me-up. Whether you are kick starting a workout or a workday, CHEW SUP the way you want, when you want. 

WHY CHEW SUP?

Chew SUP's delish gummies on the go. SUP FIT Caffeine Energy is packed with 80mg of Caffeine per serve for:

  • An afternoon pick-me-up
  • Fuel for your active lifestyle
  • An energy buzz
  • An energy hit equivalent to one cup of instant coffee per serve (5 gummies = approximately 80mg of Caffeine)
CHEWSUP

Size: 65 Gummies

KEY FEATURES

• An afternoon pick-me-up
• Fuel for your active lifestyle
• An energy buzz
• An energy hit equivalent to one cup of instant coffee per serve (5 gummies = approx. 80mg of Caffeine)
• 99% Sugar Free

Warnings

This food is not a sole source of nutrition and should be consumed in conjunction with a nutritious diet and exercise program. Not suitable for children under 15 years of age or pregnant women: should be used under medical or dietetic supervision. Contains caffeine. Should not be taken by individuals sensitive to caffeine. It is vital to consume ample water to avoid dehydration. Formulated Supplementary Sports Food. Excess consumption may have laxative effect. Do not use if tamper evident seal is broken or missing. Reseal immediately after use.

Ingredients

Sweetener (maltitol), Maize starch, Gelatine, Water, Acidity regulator (330, 331), Flavourings (natural mixed berry, bitterness masker), Natural encapsulated caffeine, Natural colour (120), Glazing agent (coconut oil, beeswax, carnauba wax), Cyanocobalamin

Contains: CONTAINS CAFFEINE

Allergen Contains: Caffeine

Allergen Free From: Gluten

Directions

Recommended for adults only and not to exceed 5 gummies per day. Please keep away from children.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25oC
